Package: uwinspatialtools
Type: Package
Title: Summarises spatial data in a specified buffer around points for rasters and shapefiles
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mason Fidino
Maintainer: Mason Fidino <mfidino@lpzoo.org>
Description: For the Urban Wildlife Information Network (UWIN),
    we often have to summarise data around camera trapping locations
    for varying analyses. The functions here do just that.
